    <item>
      <title>拜登国情咨文演讲的要点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/key-takeaways-from-biden-s-2024-state-of-the-union-speech-to-congress</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登将自己定位为抵御民主威胁浪潮的堡垒，并将他的前任唐纳德·特朗普描绘成应对这些危险负责的人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/key-takeaways-from-biden-s-2024-state-of-the-union-speech-to-congress</guid>
