    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度在全国大选前大幅削减烹饪天然气价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/india-slashes-cooking-gas-prices-ahead-of-national-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪在 X（前身为 Twitter）上宣布，印度已将液化石油气钢瓶价格下调 100 卢比，以减轻家庭经济负担。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/india-slashes-cooking-gas-prices-ahead-of-national-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 04:02:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乔治·桑托斯宣布再次竞选纽约州众议院席位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/george-santos-announces-another-run-for-a-new-york-house-seat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约共和党人乔治桑托斯周四宣布，在去年 12 月被同事驱逐后，他将再次竞选纽约众议院席位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/george-santos-announces-another-run-for-a-new-york-house-seat</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 03:22:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
